WEBVTT

00:04.720 --> 00:06.470
Previously on Billions...

00:06.470 --> 00:08.595
Dr. Rhoades, your medical
license is under review.

00:08.595 --> 00:10.136
I'm sorry. Why?

00:10.136 --> 00:12.220
There have been
accusations of malpractice.

00:12.220 --> 00:14.220
You reported me
to the Medical Board?

00:14.220 --> 00:15.553
Yes, I did.

00:15.553 --> 00:17.553
Are you going to say
it wasn't warranted?

00:17.553 --> 00:20.762
Help me, Chuck,
or I'm fucking lost.

00:20.762 --> 00:22.095
Make them drop the inquest?

00:22.095 --> 00:24.011
Is something you can do.

00:24.011 --> 00:25.887
Tomorrow is
Rebecca Cantu's first day

00:25.887 --> 00:27.220
as CEO of Saler's.

00:27.220 --> 00:29.512
I want it to be
a bad one for her.

00:29.512 --> 00:31.512
I'm going to need to withdraw
from the board.

00:31.512 --> 00:33.345
Me, too.
How come?

00:33.345 --> 00:34.679
We sold our shares.

00:34.679 --> 00:35.720
Who'd you sell to?

00:35.720 --> 00:37.470
Taylor Mason.

00:37.470 --> 00:39.053
I'm here to apply for a wiretap.

00:39.053 --> 00:40.720
On Chuck Rhoades,
for public corruption.

00:40.720 --> 00:42.970
The relationship between
the good judge and Mr. Rhoades

00:42.970 --> 00:44.679
is all the more reason
why the wire is needed.

00:44.679 --> 00:45.845
Well played.

00:45.845 --> 00:47.303
You have your wire.

00:47.303 --> 00:52.345
I have run into a financing snag
with my development.

00:52.345 --> 00:54.762
So how are we going to
skin this...

00:54.762 --> 00:58.053
Now have a seat, Mr. Secretary,
we have much to discuss.

00:58.053 --> 00:59.762
Positive news, Dad.

00:59.762 --> 01:02.220
Qatar State Bank is going to be
taken off the restricted list

01:02.220 --> 01:04.512
and it's ready to give you
a sweetheart of a loan.

01:04.512 --> 01:06.428
Are you sure about this?

01:06.428 --> 01:08.679
Got it straight from
the Secretary Of The Treasury.

01:08.679 --> 01:11.261
In the last year,
your house was paid off.

01:11.261 --> 01:13.970
Yeah, my wife
came into some money.

01:13.970 --> 01:17.428
I'm sorry, do you...
do you want a towel, or...

01:17.428 --> 01:19.261
I'm good.

01:19.261 --> 01:20.637
The Medical Board...

01:20.637 --> 01:22.261
I'm sorry, Wend.

01:22.261 --> 01:23.970
You're gonna have to
take your chances with them.

01:23.970 --> 01:26.220
Then I know it couldn't be done.

01:28.000 --> 01:34.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:55.595 --> 01:57.637
The bank I moved
off the restricted list...

01:57.637 --> 01:59.220
Qatar State Bank...

01:59.220 --> 02:00.512
That's right.
A report came in.

02:00.512 --> 02:02.136
I'm gonna have to move it

02:02.136 --> 02:03.220
back onto the restricted list.

02:03.220 --> 02:05.095
Shit.

02:05.095 --> 02:07.136
We need to meet.
Your father too.

02:07.136 --> 02:09.303
How about New Year's Day?

02:09.303 --> 02:11.595
Things will be quiet...

02:26.720 --> 02:28.011
Happy New Year.

02:28.011 --> 02:30.512
Totally.
And to you.

02:30.512 --> 02:32.095
Just how I planned to spend it.

02:33.303 --> 02:34.720
Where'd he pull you from?

02:34.720 --> 02:36.011
Turks. You?

02:36.011 --> 02:37.512
St. Barths.

02:37.512 --> 02:38.679
I don't mind.

02:38.679 --> 02:40.261
If it wasn't for this job,
the only way

02:40.261 --> 02:42.261
I'd see St. Barths
is on the Travel Channel.

02:42.261 --> 02:44.178
If I could afford cable.
Come on.

03:03.804 --> 03:05.970
I can win, right?

03:05.970 --> 03:09.011
We wouldn't be prepping
if we didn't think...

03:09.011 --> 03:10.095
Shit.

03:10.095 --> 03:12.512
You don't think I can win.

03:12.512 --> 03:15.261
Would Axe be Skyping in if
he didn't think there was a...

03:15.261 --> 03:17.512
Better if he were here.

03:17.512 --> 03:21.428
Always is. But the boys
had their hearts set on Fiji.

03:21.428 --> 03:24.053
Skype is not the same.

03:24.053 --> 03:25.470
But I guess it'll be fine.

03:25.470 --> 03:27.470
Has to be better than fine.

03:27.470 --> 03:29.970
You've got to treat today
like the real thing.

03:29.970 --> 03:31.595
We're going to
make it hard on you.

03:31.595 --> 03:33.261
Because when you face
the Medical Board,

03:33.261 --> 03:35.762
and your license is at stake,
it'll be brutal.

03:35.762 --> 03:37.512
These are smart people.

03:37.512 --> 03:39.053
Can I win?

03:39.053 --> 03:41.929
You have to convince the Board
that your work with Taylor,

03:41.929 --> 03:45.428
with all the people here, isn't
part of your medical practice.

03:45.428 --> 03:46.762
That the sessions aren't.

03:46.762 --> 03:49.720
That they are
performance coaching sessions.

03:49.720 --> 03:52.595
That Taylor wasn't a patient,
but rather a client,

03:52.595 --> 03:55.762
who doesn't enjoy
doctor-patient confidentiality...

03:55.762 --> 03:57.553
Orrin.

03:57.553 --> 03:59.970
Can. I. Win?

03:59.970 --> 04:02.261
I'll let you know
when we're done today.

04:12.762 --> 04:16.428
Old friends become enemies,
old enemies become new...

04:16.428 --> 04:18.178
We were never friends.

04:18.178 --> 04:20.011
So, when do we get
this thing started...

04:20.011 --> 04:21.595
I know: you only have
the morning to give...

04:21.595 --> 04:24.387
No. I'm eager. Eager to get you
free of this, is all.

04:24.387 --> 04:26.970
As long as it can be
'accomplished by midday repast.'

04:28.553 --> 04:30.804
Well, we're all here,
so let's get started... Mm.

04:30.804 --> 04:32.970
Well.
It's about time.

04:32.970 --> 04:34.970
Been waiting on you.

04:34.970 --> 04:37.679
You're here!

04:37.679 --> 04:40.470
Let's win this thing.

04:45.845 --> 04:48.303
Yeah.
Helo landed a few hours ago.

04:48.303 --> 04:49.929
The waves were a little big.

04:49.929 --> 04:51.178
Gordie got scraped on a coral.

04:51.178 --> 04:53.345
Deanie's surfboard
got broken in half.

04:53.345 --> 04:55.553
We have front-row seats at
the Rangers game tomorrow,

04:55.553 --> 04:57.303
they were happy
to bug out of there.

05:06.470 --> 05:09.637
You weren't expected to be here.

05:09.637 --> 05:12.011
Fair enough.

05:12.011 --> 05:15.512
Dr. Rhoades,
we're holding this inquest

05:15.512 --> 05:17.345
over your severe
ethics violation

05:17.345 --> 05:19.804
and misuse of patient records.

05:19.804 --> 05:22.845
Tell us about the nature of
your sessions with Taylor Mason.

05:22.845 --> 05:25.095
I never discuss what I talk
about with patients.

05:25.095 --> 05:26.845
So Taylor was your patient?

05:26.845 --> 05:29.345
If we find there was
a breach, it was a breach of

05:29.345 --> 05:31.178
doctor-patient
confidentiality then.

05:31.178 --> 05:32.178
Client.
I meant client.

05:32.178 --> 05:34.220
Taylor was a client

05:34.220 --> 05:36.929
in my performance enhancement
practice.

05:40.428 --> 05:42.512
We have to assume
Wendy Rhoades will be

05:42.512 --> 05:44.720
buttoned down, focused,
primed to go.

05:44.720 --> 05:46.929
I rattled her.
She was rattled.

05:46.929 --> 05:48.387
And then I rattled her.

05:48.387 --> 05:50.220
But I suspect, as Sara does,
that Wendy will rally.

05:50.220 --> 05:52.053
And that she'll slay.

05:52.053 --> 05:53.553
So we have to slay harder.

05:53.553 --> 05:54.929
You do, Taylor.

05:54.929 --> 05:56.470
Tell me to slay, I'll slay.

05:56.470 --> 05:58.303
Let's get into it.

06:00.136 --> 06:02.387
Slayed me last night.

06:02.387 --> 06:04.970
What did you all do
for New Year's Eve?

06:06.303 --> 06:08.679
I mostly stayed in
and did some reading.

06:08.679 --> 06:09.929
Same.

06:09.929 --> 06:11.762
You stayed in.
That doesn't sound like...

06:11.762 --> 06:13.345
Not same.

06:13.345 --> 06:15.053
I just mean, I didn't do much.

06:15.053 --> 06:17.387
Amateur night, you know?

06:17.387 --> 06:19.720
I prefer to party on the nights
they're not out.

06:19.720 --> 06:23.762
So I just hit a diner...
with some friends.

06:23.762 --> 06:25.553
A friend.

06:25.553 --> 06:28.845
Ahh, I wish I'd known you were
just chilling, Lauren.

06:32.637 --> 06:35.095
Happy New Year!
Right?

06:36.261 --> 06:40.261
Hello.

06:40.261 --> 06:42.053
This is Lonnie Watley.

06:42.053 --> 06:43.720
He was a star under Rhoades
at SDNY.

06:43.720 --> 06:46.303
Chuck trained me.
I worked closely with him.

06:46.303 --> 06:48.929
I can tell you: if he is
preparing his wife

06:48.929 --> 06:51.095
for the hearing,
she will be well-prepped.

06:51.095 --> 06:52.220
She will be ready to kill.

06:52.220 --> 06:54.178
And she will say absolutely

06:54.178 --> 06:56.845
anything she needs to,
in order to win.

06:56.845 --> 06:58.470
True or not.

06:58.470 --> 07:00.220
What is your relationship
with them now?

07:00.220 --> 07:02.261
I need to know that...
Do they have hooks in me?

07:02.261 --> 07:04.720
No. They don't.

07:04.720 --> 07:07.220
Sara relayed to me what happened
between you and Wendy.

07:07.220 --> 07:09.011
And my experience was similar.

07:09.011 --> 07:11.220
Brought close
just to be expelled.

07:11.220 --> 07:12.762
Like Sammy Hagar in Van Halen.

07:12.762 --> 07:15.845
Because, in the end,
the Rhoades' only really

07:15.845 --> 07:17.261
take care of the Rhoades'.

07:17.261 --> 07:19.303
Sounds a lot like the Axelrods.

07:19.303 --> 07:21.303
Either way, let's go get 'em.

07:21.303 --> 07:23.637
We will.
But you should know:

07:23.637 --> 07:26.053
if you pursue this
it's not risk-free for you.

07:26.053 --> 07:28.011
I'm not afraid of
an attack from them...

07:28.011 --> 07:30.136
If you appear
and testify against Wendy,

07:30.136 --> 07:31.804
they could introduce
information about you,

07:31.804 --> 07:33.637
information that you
don't want out there.

07:33.637 --> 07:36.345
Shit gets written down.
Leaks happen.

07:36.345 --> 07:39.136
Suddenly your character and
your conduct's being questioned.

07:39.136 --> 07:41.053
That's how they roll.

07:41.053 --> 07:42.428
We don't need our investors

07:42.428 --> 07:43.762
learning about
your personal demons...

07:43.762 --> 07:45.387
Is this something you want to
consider, Taylor?

07:45.387 --> 07:48.011
It's worth considering...

07:48.011 --> 07:50.470
And now we have.
We may come back to it.

07:50.470 --> 07:51.887
But first, let's figure out

07:51.887 --> 07:53.679
how to strip Wendy
of her goddamn license.

07:53.679 --> 07:56.512
You know how we win?
'Cause I know how we win.

07:56.512 --> 07:57.970
We make it so Taylor
doesn't show up.

07:57.970 --> 08:00.095
They stop cooperating
with the Medical Board.

08:00.095 --> 08:02.011
It's true,
if Taylor didn't appear,

08:02.011 --> 08:03.595
or refused to state,
on the record,

08:03.595 --> 08:06.303
what Wendy did...
This matter disappears.

08:06.303 --> 08:07.553
That's not going to happen,
though.

08:07.553 --> 08:09.553
Well. Maybe I could
induce it to happen.

08:09.553 --> 08:11.345
Offer them something they need.

08:11.345 --> 08:13.929
Create leverage.
You know, what I do.

08:13.929 --> 08:15.679
Oooh...
I can't recommend...

08:15.679 --> 08:17.053
Risky move, Bobby.

08:17.053 --> 08:18.637
Agreed.
If Taylor doesn't go for it,

08:18.637 --> 08:21.303
and instead takes it to
the Board, we're fucked worse.

08:21.303 --> 08:23.845
Well, Charl, none of this would
have happened in the first place

08:23.845 --> 08:25.762
if you would have done
what you were asked.

08:25.762 --> 08:27.053
Taylor should be dealing with

08:27.053 --> 08:28.679
their own legal problems
right now...

08:28.679 --> 08:31.220
Oh. I hardly think I'm to blame
on this one, Bub.

08:31.220 --> 08:33.345
Your gang war resulted
in extra bodies...

08:33.345 --> 08:35.845
Stop.

08:35.845 --> 08:37.679
Taylor won't be bought,
won't be moved,

08:37.679 --> 08:39.386
and trying will only
make it worse.

08:39.386 --> 08:42.511
I can't let anyone engage
and ask them to drop it.

08:42.511 --> 08:45.553
I won't give Taylor
the fucking satisfaction.

08:45.553 --> 08:49.261
Sorry to pull you out,
but, uh, there's an issue.

08:49.261 --> 08:51.512
Mm.

09:01.637 --> 09:03.470
What do you got?

09:04.887 --> 09:06.095
Fuck me.

09:06.095 --> 09:07.553
What is it?

09:07.553 --> 09:09.261
A shitty New Year's present.

09:09.261 --> 09:10.887
It's a Picasso... Boy With Pipe.

09:10.887 --> 09:12.553
It's also a huge
fucking tax problem.

09:12.553 --> 09:14.512
Once you sign that, I've got
seventeen more crates

09:14.512 --> 09:16.595
scheduled to come to you
after the holiday.

09:16.595 --> 09:18.595
I'm not signing that.

09:18.595 --> 09:21.053
Well. You got to.
To take possession.

09:21.053 --> 09:22.762
You busy today?

09:22.762 --> 09:24.470
No, but I'd like to be done.
You know.

09:24.470 --> 09:26.178
Go home and watch a bowl game.

09:26.178 --> 09:29.261
Oh, yeah, sure.

09:29.261 --> 09:34.261
That is a thousand bucks...

09:34.261 --> 09:37.512
And a few more for them...

09:37.512 --> 09:39.387
I need you to wait here awhile.

09:39.387 --> 09:42.720
Ho, a day changer.
Alright.

09:42.720 --> 09:45.637
Okay.

09:45.637 --> 09:48.261
Get him a chair, a coffee,
some food... whatever he wants.

09:48.261 --> 09:49.929
Set up the game
on the laptop for him.

09:49.929 --> 09:51.595
This may take a minute.

09:54.762 --> 09:57.762
Right now that painting
and 17 others like it

09:57.762 --> 10:00.011
are gonna run over me
like a Mack truck.

10:00.011 --> 10:03.595
I need you to get Sean Ayles in
here now... this is his fuck-up.

10:03.595 --> 10:04.929
Not that he'll be
able to solve it.

10:04.929 --> 10:06.720
So get Victor in here too.
Fast.

10:06.720 --> 10:08.762
I will.

10:13.053 --> 10:14.720
Judge Funt.

10:14.720 --> 10:17.887
Even though court is closed,
justice never slumbers.

10:17.887 --> 10:20.637
At the SDNY, we are always
open for business.

10:21.637 --> 10:23.929
And I'll play you today's.

10:27.720 --> 10:29.387
The bank I moved
off the restricted list...

10:29.387 --> 10:30.679
Qatar State Bank...

10:30.679 --> 10:32.220
That's right.
A report came in.

10:32.220 --> 10:33.553
I'm gonna have to move it

10:33.553 --> 10:34.720
back onto the restricted list.

10:34.720 --> 10:36.220
Shit.

10:36.220 --> 10:37.762
We need to meet.
Your father too.

10:37.762 --> 10:39.804
How about New Year's Day?

10:39.804 --> 10:41.261
Things will be quiet...

10:43.512 --> 10:45.762
The wiretaps on their telephones
are no longer enough.

10:45.762 --> 10:47.553
We need to step up surveillance.

10:47.553 --> 10:50.011
As you heard, Judge,
they're going to meet in person

10:50.011 --> 10:53.011
in pursuit of their crimes
and we need to be listening.

10:54.637 --> 10:57.011
The Title III intercept request.

11:00.929 --> 11:03.512
I'm going to deny
bugging the NYAG office,

11:03.512 --> 11:05.762
that's outside the pale.

11:05.762 --> 11:09.512
But I'll grant... reluctantly...

11:09.512 --> 11:13.178
Transmission bugs on Chuck
and Rhoades Sr.'s residences.

11:13.178 --> 11:14.595
Not the bedrooms.

11:14.595 --> 11:17.512
Home offices,
living spaces only.

11:17.512 --> 11:19.553
Major conditions
come along with this,

11:19.553 --> 11:21.095
on what you can listen to.

11:21.095 --> 11:22.679
Of course.

11:22.679 --> 11:26.887
Anything not case related,
and it's headphones off.

11:26.887 --> 11:30.762
And if a lawyer is present, then
the recording stops absolutely

11:30.762 --> 11:33.553
to protect attorney-client
privilege.

11:33.553 --> 11:35.470
We'll put in a taint team...

11:35.470 --> 11:37.887
An FBI agent and an
Assistant US Attorney here...

11:37.887 --> 11:39.303
Who will decide what is within

11:39.303 --> 11:41.136
and what is outside
the scope of privilege.

11:41.136 --> 11:42.929
Good.

11:42.929 --> 11:46.011
They only pass on what
you're allowed to hear.

11:46.011 --> 11:49.887
You violate this, your case
is on a road to nowhere.

11:49.887 --> 11:51.720
Thank you, Judge.

11:58.220 --> 12:00.595
Ah. Good day for you
and your case...

12:00.595 --> 12:02.011
Dancshazy can pick the agent...

12:02.011 --> 12:04.095
...you'll run the taint team.

12:04.095 --> 12:06.845
Hold up.
That idea is nicht gut.

12:06.845 --> 12:08.845
It's supposed to be somebody
not involved with the case...

12:08.845 --> 12:10.261
You're not.
I'm running the case.

12:12.387 --> 12:14.845
You oversaw a surveillance,

12:14.845 --> 12:16.720
sat in on a meeting or two,
loose facts.

12:16.720 --> 12:18.220
You're unbiased.

12:18.220 --> 12:19.929
We both know that I have done
more than that,

12:19.929 --> 12:21.929
but you better believe
that I am unbiased.

12:21.929 --> 12:23.595
And you'd better not
be expecting to play

12:23.595 --> 12:25.762
the wink and nudge game with me.

12:25.762 --> 12:27.762
Or that I'll compromise
my integrity.

12:27.762 --> 12:31.095
It's because I know
you won't compromise, Kate.

12:31.095 --> 12:33.095
Anyone else in that office
I could force to bend over.

12:33.095 --> 12:34.053
You won't.

12:34.053 --> 12:35.595
Damn straight I won't.

12:35.595 --> 12:37.637
Because I am not going to jail.

12:37.637 --> 12:40.762
And I'm not coming to visit you
there either.

12:40.762 --> 12:43.428
Give me Agent Dancshazy's
extension,

12:43.428 --> 12:45.804
I want his top Tac-Ops team

12:45.804 --> 12:47.470
planting those bugs
right away...

12:55.595 --> 12:58.637
Fact pattern:
A patient enters,

12:58.637 --> 13:02.178
complaining of an elevated HR,
say, two hundred and ten BPM.

13:02.178 --> 13:03.512
Now, you suspect that

13:03.512 --> 13:05.679
he has been doing
some kind of narcotic.

13:05.679 --> 13:09.095
What is your obligato
per the Hippocratic?

13:10.637 --> 13:11.929
Narcotics bring
the heart rate down.

13:11.929 --> 13:13.428
That's why they're called
downers.

13:13.428 --> 13:14.679
Jesus, Spyros.

13:14.679 --> 13:17.470
I don't know this Spyros
of whom you speak.

13:17.470 --> 13:20.720
I am Medical Doctor Rodizio,
as my name card clearly states...

13:20.720 --> 13:23.095
That's it, Spyros.
Now you've lost the coat.

13:23.095 --> 13:24.970
Take it off.

13:31.470 --> 13:32.970
That goes too.

13:38.345 --> 13:39.553
Back to it then.

13:39.553 --> 13:41.345
Isn't it so,
Ms. Rhoades...

13:41.345 --> 13:44.762
Dr. Rhoades.
Don't do that to them. No.

13:44.762 --> 13:46.595
Play through...
You play through...

13:46.595 --> 13:50.637
Isn't it true, Dr. Rhoades,

13:50.637 --> 13:52.178
that this isn't the first time

13:52.178 --> 13:53.970
your patient's notes
have been vulnerable

13:53.970 --> 13:55.929
and were used against
the patient themself?

13:55.929 --> 13:58.095
Sometime in the recent past
you were careless

13:58.095 --> 13:59.970
and someone in the US Attorney's
office got a hold of...

13:59.970 --> 14:01.679
Un-fucking-believable...

14:01.679 --> 14:02.845
- Whoa...
- Whoa...

14:02.845 --> 14:04.637
Whoa.
Whoa, hey, hold up.

14:04.637 --> 14:06.595
If you're going to
lose your poise that easily,

14:06.595 --> 14:07.720
I'll recommend you don't appear

14:07.720 --> 14:10.178
and take whatever decision
they hand out.

14:10.178 --> 14:12.053
It's like that commercial:
"never let 'em see you sweat."

14:12.053 --> 14:13.595
You've seen The Usual Suspects,

14:13.595 --> 14:15.345
only the guilty one can
sleep through the night.

14:15.345 --> 14:18.470
Nope. Ya gotta keep
as cool as a menthol.

14:18.470 --> 14:20.637
That's Kool with a K.

14:22.679 --> 14:24.345
Hey.

14:24.345 --> 14:25.553
Come on.

