So the house was empty.
We got up on both.

28:12.553 --> 28:16.595
You are the man!

28:16.595 --> 28:18.303
Expect a bottle in your
Christmas stocking on me.

28:18.303 --> 28:19.762
Top shelf.
Sure thing.

28:19.762 --> 28:21.053
Happy it worked out.
Yeah.

28:21.053 --> 28:22.762
One thing though:
chalk a big ring

28:22.762 --> 28:24.595
around the listening room
and taint team office.

28:24.595 --> 28:26.470
You cross that line,
Judge'll burn your case.

28:26.470 --> 28:28.553
And you with it.
You know I will.

28:34.887 --> 28:39.053
No one makes me smile
like my boy!

28:39.053 --> 28:41.553
What about that
sweet little baby girl

28:41.553 --> 28:43.261
with the champion's chin?

28:43.261 --> 28:45.595
She fills the chest with
happiness, too, of course.

28:45.595 --> 28:47.679
In a much less complicated way.

28:47.679 --> 28:50.053
She never has to perform.
Never has to achieve.

28:50.053 --> 28:52.053
Mm.
As long as she merely is,

28:52.053 --> 28:53.637
she brings joy.

28:53.637 --> 28:57.762
But you, son, bring pride
along for the journey.

28:57.762 --> 28:59.720
What the fuck kind of meds
are you on?

28:59.720 --> 29:02.261
Pure adrenaline. I've been out
walking the city today.

29:02.261 --> 29:03.428
Ah-ha.

29:03.428 --> 29:05.095
Youbetcha.

29:05.095 --> 29:07.720
Thinking of all the things
that we're going to do.

29:07.720 --> 29:10.679
And it freshens the blood
like Geritol.

29:10.679 --> 29:12.136
Uh-huh.
And, uh, Mom?

29:12.136 --> 29:13.428
She's down in Palm Beach

29:13.428 --> 29:15.261
enjoying the weather
and the shopping.

29:15.261 --> 29:16.261
Good for her.

29:16.261 --> 29:18.261
And speaking of joy.

29:18.261 --> 29:20.762
I saw your kids today.

29:20.762 --> 29:23.136
A delight!

29:23.136 --> 29:24.762
Real gentleman and lady.

29:24.762 --> 29:26.595
Well, they love
their grandfather.

29:26.595 --> 29:28.387
Cup of tea?

29:28.387 --> 29:30.470
Mm.

29:30.470 --> 29:32.345
Ira and... The Secretary?

29:32.345 --> 29:33.970
En route.

29:33.970 --> 29:35.470
Shouldn't be long.

29:44.762 --> 29:46.970
What the fuck is he doing here?

29:46.970 --> 29:49.303
Ah.
We like him again.

29:49.303 --> 29:50.804
Special project.

29:50.804 --> 29:53.679
We're good...

30:07.970 --> 30:11.178
The Italians think anyone
who puts milk on their coffee

30:11.178 --> 30:13.595
after 11AM is animale.

30:13.595 --> 30:15.887
I tend to agree.
In theory, but in reality...

30:15.887 --> 30:17.679
Just gimme the espresso.

30:17.679 --> 30:19.553
There's a guy from
the shipping company here.

30:19.553 --> 30:21.679
Another guy.
Kind of demanding to see you.

30:31.970 --> 30:33.637
I can't afford
to have my only guys

30:33.637 --> 30:35.845
working the holiday
pulled out of service.

30:35.845 --> 30:38.053
You told him I spritzed you?

30:39.261 --> 30:40.720
He tells me everything.

30:40.720 --> 30:43.595
And I tell my brother-in-law
everything.

30:43.595 --> 30:45.011
Don't you want to know

30:45.011 --> 30:46.679
what my brother-in-law
does for a living?

30:46.679 --> 30:47.762
Do I?

30:47.762 --> 30:49.387
He works in a little
outfit called

30:49.387 --> 30:51.970
United States Customs
and Border Protection.

30:51.970 --> 30:54.387
Well, isn't that a sweet set-up.

30:54.387 --> 30:56.095
It really is.

30:56.095 --> 30:58.053
Ayles!

31:00.303 --> 31:03.220
Will you take this gentleman
somewhere to talk in private.

31:03.220 --> 31:05.220
Make sure he's not recording it.

31:05.220 --> 31:07.303
And then make him happy.

31:07.303 --> 31:10.553
I am grateful
of the opportunity to,

31:10.553 --> 31:13.053
as they say at the rummy table,
get off the schneid.

31:13.053 --> 31:15.512
Sir?

31:15.512 --> 31:18.428
If any other guys like you
show up to shake me down,

31:18.428 --> 31:19.762
I start burning paintings.

31:19.762 --> 31:20.970
I'd rather lose money
than deal with

31:20.970 --> 31:23.553
this bullshit another minute.

31:29.512 --> 31:30.762
HNY.

31:30.762 --> 31:32.095
Why are we here?

31:32.095 --> 31:34.178
Well. I didn't think
you'd want all of them...

31:34.178 --> 31:36.053
Getting a jump-start
on the year ahead of you.

31:36.053 --> 31:37.595
But why are they here?

31:37.595 --> 31:40.720
They don't want me getting
a jump-start on them.

31:59.762 --> 32:01.887
Why'd you really come back?

32:01.887 --> 32:04.887
How many margaritas and
piÃ±a coladas can a man drink?

32:04.887 --> 32:07.261
When it's the man I'm looking
at, a hell of a lot.

32:07.261 --> 32:09.929
And how long can you stay in
the sun before getting burned?

32:12.804 --> 32:14.804
What time is it?

32:14.804 --> 32:18.303
Yes.
The Patek is gone.

32:18.303 --> 32:19.929
Your dad gave that to you,
didn't he?

32:19.929 --> 32:21.762
Bequeathed it
ahead of his death.

32:21.762 --> 32:24.387
Quite a dry-eyed moment
for him...

32:24.387 --> 32:27.261
Estate planning and so forth...

32:27.261 --> 32:31.387
But for me,
it meant a great deal.

32:31.387 --> 32:32.804
A great deal.

32:32.804 --> 32:35.762
Where is it?

32:35.762 --> 32:37.136
Somewhere in South Beach.

32:37.136 --> 32:39.428
Or maybe already riding
the Silk Road

32:39.428 --> 32:41.929
to some exotic destination.

32:41.929 --> 32:43.470
You didn't get so drunk
you sold it.

32:43.470 --> 32:45.303
Nope.

32:45.303 --> 32:47.261
Went back to the hotel room
with a young lady I had met.

32:47.261 --> 32:49.345
A yacht girl.
But not really.

32:49.345 --> 32:51.136
She was...

32:51.136 --> 32:52.762
I thought she was special.

32:52.762 --> 32:54.178
How young?

32:54.178 --> 32:55.762
Does it matter?

32:55.762 --> 32:58.595
She had an old soul...

32:58.595 --> 33:00.136
22.

33:01.762 --> 33:03.345
I thought I liked her.

33:05.679 --> 33:07.178
I did like her.

33:07.178 --> 33:09.178
And then?

33:09.178 --> 33:12.178
Passed out. Woke up,
she, and the watch, were gone.

33:12.178 --> 33:14.553
You call the police?

33:14.553 --> 33:17.512
Too embarrassed.

33:17.512 --> 33:19.387
Too sad.

33:19.387 --> 33:22.178
Put a real dent in
my faith in humanity.

33:22.178 --> 33:24.178
It's sweet you still have some.

33:28.679 --> 33:30.345
Lemme make a call.

33:30.345 --> 33:31.428
It'll make you feel better.

33:31.428 --> 33:33.011
Watch dealer?

33:33.011 --> 33:35.220
Close.
She's a specialist.

33:35.220 --> 33:36.387
In what?

33:36.387 --> 33:38.053
Restoring faith in humanity.

33:44.387 --> 33:46.261
Let's dispense with
the pleasantries

33:46.261 --> 33:48.053
and ball tickling, shall we.

33:48.053 --> 33:50.470
What's this about a problem?

33:50.470 --> 33:53.136
Political winds shift,
I have to shift with them.

33:53.136 --> 33:55.345
And the Middle East is
the windiest of them all.

33:55.345 --> 33:57.095
Qatar is persona non grata
again.

33:57.095 --> 33:59.762
That may be. But your tit's
in the wringer...

33:59.762 --> 34:01.136
My son put it there...

34:01.136 --> 34:02.637
So you'd better not
shift too much

34:02.637 --> 34:05.053
or it'll get ripped off.
He'll tear it off.

34:05.053 --> 34:08.219
What he's saying in
his inimitable way is:

34:08.219 --> 34:12.804
what can we do to keep
the financing in place?

34:12.804 --> 34:16.303
Okay. Crap.
Okay.

34:16.303 --> 34:17.887
Perhaps I can paper an exception

34:17.887 --> 34:19.844
and bury it deep in
the halls of government.

34:19.844 --> 34:21.428
But for that,
we have to go beyond

34:21.428 --> 34:23.512
the parameters of
the original deal.

34:23.512 --> 34:26.053
I'm not gonna stay neutral,
I need to go positive.

34:26.053 --> 34:28.094
- Hold on...
- What are you saying?

34:28.094 --> 34:30.094
If the loan I help facilitate

34:30.094 --> 34:32.844
results in your development,
I want to...

34:35.594 --> 34:37.679
From my bowl?

34:37.679 --> 34:38.804
- Mm-hmm.
- Oh my god...

34:38.804 --> 34:40.679
Quiet, Ira.
How much?

34:43.261 --> 34:45.094
Fucking shakedown.

34:45.094 --> 34:47.178
In line with standard
finder's fees.

34:47.178 --> 34:48.428
He's right.

34:48.428 --> 34:50.512
Maybe he is.
But I don't have to like it.

34:50.512 --> 34:54.011
Whatever our understanding,
it can't just be verbal...

34:54.011 --> 34:58.136
Ah.
I've taken the liberty.

34:58.136 --> 35:00.136
For our comfort...

35:00.136 --> 35:02.595
All we need to do is...

35:02.595 --> 35:06.804
And then everyone is nice.

35:24.804 --> 35:26.303
Perhaps you'd like
to take these...

35:26.303 --> 35:28.053
I'm not touching
that fucking thing.

35:28.053 --> 35:30.178
Suit yourself.
I'll just put them in my safe.

35:30.178 --> 35:32.512
One second, fast guy.

35:46.303 --> 35:48.428
There'll be no changing it
after the fact now.

35:48.428 --> 35:50.970
I need to go back to DC.

35:50.970 --> 35:53.053
I have work to do.

35:53.053 --> 35:55.345
Gentlemen.

36:02.595 --> 36:04.679
Now that it's just
the three of us, I have to say,

36:04.679 --> 36:07.011
I did not know the nature of
that conversation beforehand...

36:07.011 --> 36:08.470
And further...

36:08.470 --> 36:10.512
You can do all the mewling
you want about matters legal

36:10.512 --> 36:12.345
once I get this copy
locked in my safe.

36:12.345 --> 36:15.011
And then, Dad.
You have to tell him everything.

36:15.011 --> 36:17.595
So he can defend us,
whatever may come.

36:17.595 --> 36:20.053
You mean about the idiot
who stands to lose the most?

36:20.053 --> 36:22.011
Can I really... Yes.

36:22.011 --> 36:23.303
I can't listen to future plans.

36:23.303 --> 36:24.845
But the things
you've already done.

36:24.845 --> 36:26.887
And the people with whom
you've done 'em,

36:26.887 --> 36:27.804
that I need to know.

36:38.553 --> 36:41.637
I've taken the liberty.

36:41.637 --> 36:42.929
For our comfort...

36:42.929 --> 36:44.970
All we need to do is...

36:44.970 --> 36:47.011
This is fucking incredible.

36:47.011 --> 36:48.345
What... What am I hearing...

36:48.345 --> 36:49.929
That they've entered
into a conspiracy?

36:49.929 --> 36:52.136
Fraud.
A quid pro quo deal.

36:52.136 --> 36:53.428
International banking
violations.

36:53.428 --> 36:55.011
Money laundering to follow.
Shh...

36:55.011 --> 36:56.136
What's that rustling?

36:56.136 --> 36:57.887
Did they paper
this fucking deal?

36:57.887 --> 36:59.387
Perhaps you'd like
to hold these...

36:59.387 --> 37:01.470
I'm not touching
that fucking thing.

37:01.470 --> 37:02.637
Suit yourself.
I'll just put them in my safe.

37:02.637 --> 37:04.553
Stay tuned for this next part.

37:04.553 --> 37:06.136
Now that it's just
the three of us, I have to say,

37:06.136 --> 37:07.762
I did not know
the nature of that conversation

37:07.762 --> 37:09.345
beforehand...
